&reftitle.description;
public mixedVtiful\Kernel\Excel::evaluateFormula stringformula
Evaluates a spreadsheet formula and returns its computed result. Cell references are resolved against the cells already written to the worksheet currently open for writing; in constant-memory mode, references to already flushed cells resolve as blank.

&reftitle.parameters;


  formula

   The formula expression to evaluate, with or without a leading equals sign.
